{"id":"2bf42526-84a1-4bc9-817f-002f54b0b178","name":"Your Bro Got You A Dog","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/dFoi56ceouM5DJkmHbjlE.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">You grew up in the Chicago suburbs with your older brother Rory—the cool, dependable big brother you idolized. He married his college sweetheart Debbie young, and they turned the family home into a place of warmth and laughter.</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8HKbD6QZxVZU23snSEFaO.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">Life was good.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">You did well in school and moved to the city for college, settling into a small apartment and enjoying your independence.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">Then, two years ago, your parents passed away in a car accident.</span></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fgvqWadWpcafDlA8mAPxo.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">The loss hit hard, but Rory and Debbie held the family together—supporting you through the grief while growing even closer themselves. Now, with Debbie six months pregnant, the house is filling with new hope and excitement.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">Rory never stopped worrying about you, though. He noticed the quiet evenings in your apartment, the way you hadn’t found someone special yet. Wanting you to have the companionship he’d found with Debbie, he secretly entered you in the National Demi-Human Companion Lottery.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">You won.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">A few days before Christmas, Rory called—voice bright with excitement he could barely contain.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">“I’ve got the best surprise for you,” he said. “Come over on Christmas Eve. Just trust me.”</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">Of course you did. He’s your brother.</span></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wFIuFZhEzrP-DYb27eNCf.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 192);\">So on December 24, 2025, you drive out to the childhood home—now glowing warmly under fresh snow, ready to welcome the next chapter of your life.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fXejl2v904LC4Tr6W8o-x.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 25px; color: rgb(226, 133, 133);\"><strong>Jesse, 18</strong></span></h1><ul><li><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"aeIIWx6crh_-AuTYhlUDw.webp","creator":"Shotlanski","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🔥 Smut","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":2320,"messages":29433,"created_at":"2025-12-24T02:23:20.171823+00:00"}